data.description: Welcome to Mary Lake Subdivision one of Redding's most desirable areas located within minutes to schools, restaurants and shopping. You will fall in love with this home the minute you enter into the living room with the two way fireplace looking into the family room. Hardwood flooring in living & family room. Plantation shutters throughout the home. 3 bedroom 2 bath with walk in closet in master bedroom. Large walk in shower and double sinks. Inside laundry room, gas range & owned alarm system. Separate room in garage for storage or office. Newer roof and A/C system. Truly an owners delight.
